  "detailed_description": "<h1>Don't forget to wishlist</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/fea65f0f8fcb07d19357ee34639068e0.avif?t=1697076851\" width=400 height=150 /></span></p><br><h1>More Source Byte Games:</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>GeoJelly </strong>is a platformer where you are limited to jumping to escape the laboratory. You'll face the challenge of accurately measuring your jumps to land where you intend to... given you endure the difficulty of the test chambers. To unlock levels you have to collect diamonds. The more diamonds the more levels you unlock.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔥Gameplay:🔥</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy Mode with Aim and hard mode.             <br></li><li>You don't have to go through the levels in order.<br></li><li>Think twice before jump.<br></li><li>Easy Levels and Very hard levels.<br></li><li>Hold to charge, then let go to jump!<br></li><li>Many unique obstacles await you -> Black holes, Jump Pads,  windmills, Cannons, and Spikes. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 50 Levels with different themes.<br></li><li>Lots of logical puzzles.<br></li><li> Game for many hours.<br></li><li>You can become a speedrunner in GeoJelly</li></ul><br><strong>Hold to charge, then let go to jump! </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/5118885c296858e77e765c7e2311bf5b.poster.avif?t=1697076851\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/5118885c296858e77e765c7e2311bf5b.webm?t=1697076851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/5118885c296858e77e765c7e2311bf5b.mp4?t=1697076851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>- Seems simple? It's only looking simple... hehe</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>GeoJelly </strong>is a platformer where you are limited to jumping to escape the laboratory. You'll face the challenge of accurately measuring your jumps to land where you intend to... given you endure the difficulty of the test chambers. To unlock levels you have to collect diamonds. The more diamonds the more levels you unlock.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🔥Gameplay:🔥</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy Mode with Aim and hard mode.             <br></li><li>You don't have to go through the levels in order.<br></li><li>Think twice before jump.<br></li><li>Easy Levels and Very hard levels.<br></li><li>Hold to charge, then let go to jump!<br></li><li>Many unique obstacles await you -> Black holes, Jump Pads,  windmills, Cannons, and Spikes. </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 50 Levels with different themes.<br></li><li>Lots of logical puzzles.<br></li><li> Game for many hours.<br></li><li>You can become a speedrunner in GeoJelly</li></ul><br><strong>Hold to charge, then let go to jump! </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/5118885c296858e77e765c7e2311bf5b.poster.avif?t=1697076851\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/5118885c296858e77e765c7e2311bf5b.webm?t=1697076851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208040/extras/5118885c296858e77e765c7e2311bf5b.mp4?t=1697076851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>- Seems simple? It's only looking simple... hehe</i>",
